7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:23:\"Magento Web Development\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"Boost Magento 2 Store Sales\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"Increase Store Sales\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"Magento 2 Extensions\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Magento 2 Store\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/?p=46032\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:610:\"<p>Do you run an eCommerce store and want to boost the online sales during the holiday season? With Christmas and New Year around the corner, website owners are looking for new ways to attract more customers and make huge sales. Christmas is the right time to promote your products and services to the online world. </p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/magento/boost-sales-in-holiday-season/\">Boost Your Magento 2 Store Sales In Holiday Season [Most Profitable Tips]</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Mayur Dhudasia\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21633:\"<p>Do you run an <strong>eCommerce store</strong> and want to <strong>boost the online sales</strong> during the holiday season? </p>\n<p>With <strong>Christmas</strong> and <strong>New Year</strong> around the corner, website owners are looking for new ways to attract more customers and make huge sales. Christmas is the right time to promote your products and services to the online world.</p>\n<p>Whether you want to focus on getting your first sale or you want to increase your online sales, you should experiment with new ways to promote your products to the online world. </p>\n<h3>How to promote your products or services?</h3>\n<p>There are endless options available for promoting your products or services to make your business grow. It can be difficult to pick the best method for promotion. Depending on your business and its goals you can try one or multiple methods for promoting products on your Magento eCommerce store. </p>\n<p><b>We‚Äôve listed here seven undeniable ways in which you can promote your products:</b></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>1. Find your audience</h4>\n<p>If you want to sell your products digitally, the first and the foremost step is to <strong>identify who your target audiences are</strong>. Think of the audience who may be <strong>interested in buying</strong> your products or services. Your marketing efforts can be planned to revolve around the taste and choice of your target audience. Once you‚Äôre aware of the potential clients, it would be easier to plan marketing strategies to promote your brand.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Find-your-audience-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"Find your audience\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-47559\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Find-your-audience-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Find-your-audience-300x200.jpg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Find-your-audience-768x512.jpg 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Find-your-audience-500x333.jpg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Find-your-audience-624x416.jpg 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Find-your-audience-850x567.jpg 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Find-your-audience-366x245.jpg 366w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Find-your-audience-450x300.jpg 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>2. Social Networks</h4>\n<p>Social networks are great platforms to promote your products to the right users. Create an online presence, share and build your community to be able to market online. Facebook, Twitter, Instagram, Pinterest, and more platforms can be used for spreading the word about your business. You can also run <strong>tailored paid ads on social media</strong> to promote your brand online.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Social-Networks-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"Social Networks\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-47560\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Social-Networks-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Social-Networks-300x200.jpg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Social-Networks-768x512.jpg 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Social-Networks-500x333.jpg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Social-Networks-624x416.jpg 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Social-Networks-850x567.jpg 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Social-Networks-366x245.jpg 366w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Social-Networks-450x300.jpg 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>3. Run contests</h4>\n<p>People love contests, freebies, and discounts. These are considered to be a popular method of attracting new customers and grab the attention of existing users also. Running contests is a fun and easy way to create a buzz about your eCommerce store. You can get more traffic by giveaways and contests. Choose the right timing and invite the right people for the contests.</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Hey everybody <a href=\"https://twitter.com/WCAhmedabad?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@WCAhmedabad</a>. Have you finished lunch? Stop by our booth and take a selfie with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Solwin?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Solwin</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WCAhmedabad?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#WCAhmedabad</a> and win cool prizes!! <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/2.4/72x72/1f600.png\" alt=\"?\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> <a href=\"https://t.co/RmCQRwq5PT\">pic.twitter.com/RmCQRwq5PT</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Solwin Infotech (@SolwinInfotech) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SolwinInfotech/status/916221994613403650?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">October 6, 2017</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>4. Email Marketing</h4>\n<blockquote><p>Did you know that 42% of users purchases products at least once from the promotion emails? </p></blockquote>\n<p>Email marketing is an affordable way to promote your products and services. You can gather email IDs of your users via newsletters and keep shooting them emails about new products or promotional offers. There is no need to spend a whole day writing and sending emails. You can <strong>set up automated email campaigns</strong> and increase your revenue.  </p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>5. Blogging</h4>\n<p>Blogging isn‚Äôt dead &#8211; it still works for many brands. With the right approach, you can write blogs or <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/contact-us/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">hire a professional blogger</a> to promote the lifestyle around the products you sell. You can also try guest posting to attract more customers. Once your Magento store starts getting more traffic, you can expect more sales. </p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>6. Customer Reviews</h4>\n<p>Believe it or not, customer reviews play a major role in helping the users make the decision of buying products or services. When a user wants to purchase something, he or she would check the testimonials and reviews before buying. </p>\n<blockquote><p>85% of users are greatly influenced by online reviews.</p></blockquote>\n<p>Ask your existing customers to provide reviews for the products. It can be a good idea to offer them some discount or bonus for submitting reviews. </p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>7. In-store Promotions</h4>\n<p>In-store discounts and buy-one-get-one-free are loved by users. Customers would shop at your store when they get percentage discount at your retail store. You can also adjust your inventory and show that a limited quantity of products is available on your website shop. This will compel the users to buy those products.</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Biggest <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WordPress?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#WordPress</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Magento?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Magento</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/BlackFriday?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc