 any one or more methods of free or paid promotions for your Magento eCommerce store. </p>\n<p>Magento is a pool of opportunities for both developers and users. The right approach for <strong>Magento 2 extensions</strong> and products creates prospects for eCommerce website development. Magento is a highly flexible platform that is considered to be an appealing solution for medium and large sized businesses.</p>\n<h3>Few user-friendly extensions that can help boost your Magento 2 store sales during holiday season:</h3>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>1. Banner Slider</h4>\n<p>This is a powerful tool to <strong>promote your best products or services</strong> this holiday season. The banner slider can be added to your website to grab the attention of your customers and <strong>highlight the right products</strong> you want to promote. <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/product/magento-2-extensions/responsive-banner-slider-magento-2-extension/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Responsive Banner Slider extension</a> creates an amazing look and feels to your website. This slider extension can help you showcase your products and display the best offers on the homepage and inner pages of your website. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Responsive-Banner-Slider-M2-Extension.png\" alt=\"Responsive Banner Slider - M2 Extension\" width=\"1307\" height=\"641\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-46780\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Responsive-Banner-Slider-M2-Extension.png 1307w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Responsive-Banner-Slider-M2-Extension-300x147.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Responsive-Banner-Slider-M2-Extension-768x377.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Responsive-Banner-Slider-M2-Extension-1024x502.png 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Responsive-Banner-Slider-M2-Extension-500x245.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Responsive-Banner-Slider-M2-Extension-624x306.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Responsive-Banner-Slider-M2-Extension-850x417.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Responsive-Banner-Slider-M2-Extension-350x172.png 350w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Responsive-Banner-Slider-M2-Extension-450x221.png 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1307px) 100vw, 1307px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>2. Newsletter Popup</h4>\n<p>Newsletters can be used to <strong>communicate a custom message</strong> to your target audience. Newsletters are considered to be an important part of any marketing campaign. Displaying a newsletter popup on your online store can help you get email addresses of the subscribers. <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/product/magento-2-extensions/advanced-newsletter-popup-magento-2/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Advanced Newsletter Popup extension</a> can help the eCommerce store owners customize the popup and manage the URL also. You can add a custom message to newsletter popup and catch the attention of the visitors.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Advanced-Newsletter-M2-Extension.png\" alt=\"Advanced Newsletter - M2 Extension\" width=\"1288\" height=\"666\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-46783\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Advanced-Newsletter-M2-Extension.png 1288w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Advanced-Newsletter-M2-Extension-300x155.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Advanced-Newsletter-M2-Extension-768x397.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Advanced-Newsletter-M2-Extension-1024x529.png 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Advanced-Newsletter-M2-Extension-500x259.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Advanced-Newsletter-M2-Extension-624x323.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Advanced-Newsletter-M2-Extension-850x440.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Advanced-Newsletter-M2-Extension-350x181.png 350w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Advanced-Newsletter-M2-Extension-450x233.png 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1288px) 100vw, 1288px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>3. Share on Whatsapp</h4>\n<p>How interesting it would be if your website has a feature of sharing the product details on WhatsApp directly? Next time when a gentleman visits your store and wants to share the images and details about the shirts online, he can easily share it directly with his wife over WhatsApp and get advice as to which ones to purchase. <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/product/magento-2-extensions/share-whatsapp-magento-2/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Share on Whatsapp extension</a> button can be customized and managed from the backend of your Magento store. The product image, description, price, and URL will be shared when a user clicks on the Share button.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Share-on-Whatsapp-M2-Extension-e1542358495633.png\" alt=\"Share on Whatsapp - M2 Extension\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1041\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-46787\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Share-on-Whatsapp-M2-Extension-e1542358495633.png 1200w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Share-on-Whatsapp-M2-Extension-e1542358495633-300x260.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Share-on-Whatsapp-M2-Extension-e1542358495633-768x666.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Share-on-Whatsapp-M2-Extension-e1542358495633-1024x888.png 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Share-on-Whatsapp-M2-Extension-e1542358495633-500x434.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Share-on-Whatsapp-M2-Extension-e1542358495633-624x541.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Share-on-Whatsapp-M2-Extension-e1542358495633-850x737.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Share-on-Whatsapp-M2-Extension-e1542358495633-231x200.png 231w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Share-on-Whatsapp-M2-Extension-e1542358495633-450x390.png 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>4. Discount Coupon</h4>\n<p>Most of the online stores offer huge discounts and offers on their products and services during the holiday season. On the other hand, customers look for <strong>Christmas and New Year offers</strong> to purchase their favorite items online. <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/product/magento-2-extensions/discount-coupon-code-link-magento-2/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Discount Coupon Code Link extension</a> helps website owners to provide a unique feature to users to get discount automatically. Store owners can create and share coupon codes with customers to grab more sales and profits. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Discount-Coupon-Code-Link-M2-Extension.png\" alt=\"Discount Coupon Code Link - M2 Extension\" width=\"1307\" height=\"709\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-46798\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Discount-Coupon-Code-Link-M2-Extension.png 1307w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Discount-Coupon-Code-Link-M2-Extension-300x163.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Discount-Coupon-Code-Link-M2-Extension-768x417.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Discount-Coupon-Code-Link-M2-Extension-1024x555.png 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Discount-Coupon-Code-Link-M2-Extension-500x271.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Discount-Coupon-Code-Link-M2-Extension-624x338.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Discount-Coupon-Code-Link-M2-Extension-850x461.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Discount-Coupon-Code-Link-M2-Extension-350x190.png 350w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Discount-Coupon-Code-Link-M2-Extension-450x244.png 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1307px) 100vw, 1307px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>5. Testimonials</h4>\n<p>Reviews and testimonials play an important role in the success of an eCommerce store. Customer reviews <strong>give new visitors a reason to purchase</strong> from your store without any hesitation. The website admin can approve the testimonial and make it visible on the website. <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/product/magento-2-extensions/advanced-testimonials-magento-2/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Advanced Testimonials extension</a> prompts the customers to share their experiences about the products or services. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Advanced-Testimonials-M2-Extension-e1542365814493.png\" alt=\"Advanced Testimonials - M2 Extension\" width=\"1400\" height=\"1361\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-46801\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Advanced-Testimonials-M2-Extension-e1542365814493.png 1400w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Advanced-Testimonials-M2-Extension-e1542365814493-300x292.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Advanced-Testimonials-M2-Extension-e1542365814493-768x747.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Advanced-Testimonials-M2-Extension-e1542365814493-1024x995.png 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Advanced-Testimonials-M2-Extension-e1542365814493-500x486.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Advanced-Testimonials-M2-Extension-e1542365814493-624x607.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Advanced-Testimonials-M2-Extension-e1542365814493-850x826.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Advanced-Testimonials-M2-Extension-e1542365814493-206x200.png 206w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Advanced-Testimonials-M2-Extension-e1542365814493-450x437.png 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px\" /></p>\n<p>If you own an eCommerce store, you can start looking for these <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/magento/top-magento-2-extensions/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">best Magento 2 extensions</a> as well to add more functionality to your website and grow your business. </p>\n<h4>Conclusion:</h4>\n<p>Many <strong>Magento web developers and agencies</strong> are focusing on building extensions to help users add the required functionality to their web store. If you‚Äôre a developer and have created Magento extensions to help other developers or users around the world to add the desired functionality, then you need to find the right customers. </p>\n<p>It is important to launch Magento products and <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/seo/magneto-2-seo-tips/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">boost your sales</a> through online marketing. Look for effective ways to promote your products for an eCommerce store. With so many extensions for Magento 2 website available, you‚Äôre likely to get confused about installing the best one. Do some research online and try to find reliable Magento extensions for your eCommerce website.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/magento/boost-sales-in-holiday-season/\">Boost Your Magento 2 Store Sales In Holiday Season [Most Profitable Tips]</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:79:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/magento/boost-sales-in-holiday-season/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:74:\"15 Actionable Ecommerce Marketing Strategies to Increase Your Online Sales\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:77:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/ecommerce/ecommerce-marketing-strategies/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:86:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/ecommerce/ecommerce-marketing-strategies/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Sun, 11 Nov 2018 10:44:41 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:6:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"eCommerce\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Web Development\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19:\"Ecommerce Marketing\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:25:\"Ecommerce Marketing Guide\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"Ecommerce Marketing Strategy\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:24:\"Ecommerce Marketing Tips\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/?p=46029\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:648:\"<p>Whether you have a start-up or an established online shop, all you need is higher sales figures. However, it is a herculean task to remain competitive among thousands of eCommerce store. Your store should remain up to date with the current marketing trends, and this necessity leads you to implement effective eCommerce marketing strategies. Here </p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/ecommerce/ecommerce-marketing-strategies/\">15 Actionable Ecommerce Marketing Strategies to Increase Your Online Sales</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Sanjay Dabhoya\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22403:\"<p>Whether you have a start-up or an established online shop, all you need is higher sales figures. </p>\n<p>However, it is a herculean task to remain competitive among thousands of eCommerce store. Your store should remain up to date with the current marketing trends, and this necessity leads you to implement effective eCommerce marketing strategies. </p>\n<p>Here we give <strong>fifteen time-tested eCommerce marketing tips</strong> that can make your eCommerce store ready to deal with the growing competition:</p>\n<h3>1. Website Optimization</h3>\n<p>Let us put first things first. Your eCommerce website <strong>needs optimization</strong> for layout, language, conversion elements, and other performance parameters after launching. You need to make sure that when the visitors come to your site, they find it friendly and convenient. </p>\n<blockquote><p>Simple check-in and easy checkout processes are a must along with a pleasant look and feel to increase the web traffic.</p></blockquote>\n<p>Therefore, you must optimize your website for color, graphics, and content.</p>\n<h3>2. Content Creation</h3>\n<p>Both <strong>promotional and informative objectives</strong> are served well with a creative and original content. Setting up a relevant, unique, and yet simple content is really necessary to ensure the success of an eCommerce website.</p>\n<p>You can compel the visitors to purchase with the help of <strong>crisp and high-quality content</strong>. If you want to opt for a content marketing, your website content should be in line with the efforts put by professional content writers. </p>\n<p>You can attract and retain the customers to your website by promoting interactive content. All you need to brainstorm on the topics that can give your customers and site visitors a new perspective or new information. </p>\n<p>You can promote the online shop with blog posts, videos, newsletters, etc. and show your domain expertise with ease.  What‚Äôs more, you can get optimum results by following the <a href=\"https://www.forbes.com/sites/davelavinsky/2014/01/20/pareto-principle-how-to-use-it-to-dramatically-grow-your-business/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Pareto‚Äôs principle</a> for content, that indicates 80 percent informative and 20 percent promotional content.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_46048\" style=\"width: 570px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/The-802F20-Rule-of-content-1.png\" alt=\"80-20 Rule\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46048\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/The-802F20-Rule-of-content-1.png 560w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/The-802F20-Rule-of-content-1-300x169.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/The-802F20-Rule-of-content-1-500x281.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/The-802F20-Rule-of-content-1-350x197.png 350w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/The-802F20-Rule-of-content-1-450x253.png 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Image Source: etchrock.com</p></div>\n<h3>3. Social Media Presence</h3>\n<p>When it comes to online marketing methods, the social media network offers the most effective and yet the highly affordable platform. It is easy to establish and maintain a direct communication with your customers, visitors, and marketers on social media. </p>\n<p>You can increase the engagement and boost web traffic with the help of <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/social-media-marketing/social-media-marketing-trends/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">social media marketing</a>. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Social-Media-Presence.jpg\" alt=\"Social Media Presence\" width=\"5472\" height=\"3648\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-46054\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Social-Media-Presence.jpg 5472w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Social-Media-Presence-300x200.jpg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Social-Media-Presence-768x512.jpg 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Social-Media-Presence-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Social-Media-Presence-500x333.jpg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Social-Media-Presence-624x416.jpg 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Social-Media-Presence-850x567.jpg 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Social-Media-Presence-366x245.jpg 366w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Social-Media-Presence-450x300.jpg 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 5472px) 100vw, 5472px\" /></p>\n<p>Today, different social media channels bring people with various interests under one roof and you can build a large customer base across the world by utilizing social media.</p>\n<p>In a way, social media can assist you to grow your business by building and strengthening your brand‚Äôs reputation. You can enhance brand recognition by showing a strong social media presence. </p>\n<h3>4. Run Email and PPC Campaigns</h3>\n<p>Email is one of <strong>the cheapest and yet the most effective method</strong> to reach a huge audience online. But then, you need to be very careful about the email format and frequency, because email is a two-edged sword. </p>\n<p>If you want to address the audience properly, email marketing is a better option because you can also monitor the outcome of email marketing efforts.</p>\n<p>You can give useful content in an interactive way within your emails along with a <strong>special promotional offer</strong>. And yes, to build a substantial email list, it is a good option to offer special discounts and coupons in lieu of email sign-ups.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Google-Ads-1.jpg\" alt=\"Google Ads\" width=\"5472\" height=\"3648\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-46058\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Google-Ads-1.jpg 5472w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Google-Ads-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Google-Ads-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Google-Ads-1-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Google-Ads-1-500x333.jpg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Google-Ads-1-624x416.jpg 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Google-Ads-1-850x567.jpg 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Google-Ads-1-366x245.jpg 366w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Google-Ads-1-450x300.jpg 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 5472px) 100vw, 5472px\" />  </p>\n<p>PPC is also <strong>a productive way to promote</strong> your eCommerce shop. If you want to address a specific audience, then PPC can work wonders.</p>\n<p>You can track the result and direct your campaign accordingly with the PPC campaign. But then, you need to take care of three aspects to get the most optimum outcome: <strong>the ad</strong> (content and keyword), <strong>the offer</strong>, and <strong>the landing page</strong> (your website‚Äôs page which is linked to the PPC ad).</p>\n<h3>5. Optimize for Mobile</h3>\n<p>In today‚Äôs mobile-driven age, you must make your website responsive to any devices. As most of the searches and purchases are done through mobile devices worldwide, you need to facilitate them with a mobile-friendly website.</p>\n<p>Also, you should ensure that your customers can get what they expect from a mobile version of your website. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/mobile-site.jpg\" alt=\"mobile site\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-46062\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/mobile-site.jpg 1920w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/mobile-site-300x200.jpg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/mobile-site-768x512.jpg 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/mobile-site-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/mobile-site-500x333.jpg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/mobile-site-624x416.jpg 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/mobile-site-850x567.jpg 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/mobile-site-366x245.jpg 366w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/mobile-site-450x300.jpg 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" /></p>\n<p>A mobile-friendly website also facilitates you to apply mobile marketing techniques to target a specific audience. These days, geo-targeting concept gains ground to reach out the existing and prospective customers within a specific distance. With a mobile-optimized eCommerce site, you can leverage the benefits of this concept. </p>\n<h3>6. Target Wearables and VR devices</h3>\n<p>Let‚Äôs face it! The virtual world has made substantial progress with the advent of <strong>AR (Augmented Reality)</strong> and <strong>VR (Virtual Reality)</strong>. Any business with a futuristic vision cannot stay away from these revolutionary technologies.</p>\n<p>You should keep wearables, VR and AR devices in mind while designing and customizing the eCommerce website. There is no exaggeration in mentioning that the online business would largely rely on these technologies in the future.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_46063\" style=\"width: 1010px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/ar-vr-ecommerce.jpg\" alt=\"ar-vr ecommerce\" width=\"1000\" height=\"723\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46063\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/ar-vr-ecommerce.jpg 1000w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/ar-vr-ecommerce-300x217.jpg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/ar-vr-ecommerce-768x555.jpg 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/ar-vr-ecommerce-500x362.jpg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/ar-vr-ecommerce-624x451.jpg 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/ar-vr-ecommerce-850x615.jpg 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/ar-vr-ecommerce-277x200.jpg 277w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/ar-vr-ecommerce-450x325.jpg 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Image Source: ecommerce-nation.com</p></div>\n<h3>7.  Take Multiple Roots</h3>\n<p>How would you address a huge audience globally at once?</p>\n<p><strong>The answer is:</strong> You need to customize the UX of an eCommerce store in line with the needs of your audience.</p>\n<p>If you want to expand the outreach, it is necessary to do proper homework about the customer‚Äôs behavior. You need to offer a personal touch while taking your business to the multiple platforms. </p>\n<p>You can <strong>share videos, pictures of your employees</strong> and show the transparency of processes to attract visitors. It is openness and individual treatment that can win the hearts of your customers. </p>\n<h3>8.  Care for Abandoned Carts</h3>\n<p>One of the biggest problems in the eCommerce domain is cart abandonment. </p>\n<blockquote><p>When it becomes more frequent that the shoppers abandon their carts during purchase on your website, you need to think about it more seriously.</p></blockquote>\n<p>If you can reduce the number of abandoned carts year after year, you can increase the revenue significantly. </p>\n<p>If you really care for abandoned carts, which you should be, you should <strong>shoot a follow-up email immediately</strong> along with other relevant emails. All you need is to get the customer‚Äôs email address before the checkout process. </p>\n<p>You can also opt for ads to retarget them. <strong>For example,</strong> a <a href=\"https://blog.hootsuite.com/facebook-pixel/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook pixel</a> can help you retarget the customers who abandon their carts. Whenever they go on social media, they will immediately see your ads and may consider a purchase from your store.</p>\n<h3>9.  Opt for Upsell</h3>\n<p>Well, it is about targeting the ‚Äò<strong>buying mood</strong>‚Äô of the customers. When people by something online from any specific eCommerce platform, chances are bright that <strong>they have a euphoric feeling</strong> that comes with shopping, and they are ready to buy something related to their selected item. </p>\n<p>You can show the <strong>list of related items</strong> to the purchasing customers in a way that they feel like they are getting a better deal. It is called upselling, and Amazon utilizes it in the best possible way.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Upsells.png\" alt=\"Upsells\" width=\"836\" height=\"320\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-46086\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Upsells.png 836w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Upsells-300x115.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Upsells-768x294.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Upsells-500x191.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Upsells-624x239.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Upsells-350x134.png 350w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Upsells-450x172.png 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 836px) 100vw, 836px\" /></p>\n<p>The upselling option can enable you to increase the sales. Your customer can get a pleasant surprise while seeing the related items with better combo options. </p>\n<p>Also, you can <strong>suggest them an upgrade with a reasonable price</strong> that facilitates them to take a purchasing decision.  If you can utilize the upsell option well, it can translate into a big profit. </p>\n<h3>10. Take Help from Instagram</h3>\n<p>You may find this strategy as the weirdest of all eCommerce marketing strategies. Instagram is highly popular, and you can take an advantage of its growing penetration.</p>\n<p>You can <strong>put product images with a catchy description</strong> to give your customers and visitors a pleasant visual experience. You can also <strong>utilize the video features</strong> of this amazing platform to attract people to your online shop. </p>\n<p><b>To get the most from Instagram, you can use the tips given below:</b></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Ask your customers to post their pictures with your product</li>\n<li>Develop a unique hashtag to give your products a new identity</li>\n<li>Run contests in which you can give your products as a prize</li>\n<li>Give away your products to influencers in lieu of posting their photos</li>\n<li>Remain active in the comments section of photos and stay in touch with customers</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Remember, strong Instagram presence can lead you toward the optimum outcome.</p>\n<h3>11. Give More Power to Customers</h3>\n<p>‚Äò<strong>Wishlist</strong>‚Äô is a small function in eCommerce website with big benefits. It gives the facility to mark any item for the future if your customers do not want to buy it at the moment. You can <strong>periodically remind them</strong> about their wishlists through an email or social media. You can also send a coupon if any of the items in the wishlist have a promotional offer.</p>\n<p>What‚Äôs more, you can target your customers with items related to their wishlist. In a way, you can give more power to customers and get to know about their desires and purchase behavior. Wishlist plays a vital role in reducing the number of abandoned carts. </p>\n<h3>12. Get Product Reviews</h3>\n<p>As a customer, how would you judge any product online? Obviously, you will look at the customer reviews first.</p>\n<p>If there are more positive reviews than the negative ones, you will more likely to buy a product, and vice versa. Similarly, you must <strong>care for reviews of your products</strong> on the website. Google also counts these reviews to show the products in searches. But then, these reviews should be from genuine users of your products. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/reviews-ratings.png\" alt=\"reviews-ratings\" width=\"796\" height=\"284\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-44720\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/reviews-ratings.png 796w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/reviews-ratings-300x107.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/reviews-ratings-768x274.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/reviews-ratings-500x178.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/reviews-ratings-624x223.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/reviews-ratings-350x125.png 350w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/reviews-ratings-450x161.png 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 796px) 100vw, 796px\" /></p>\n<p>You can <strong>send a follow-up email</strong> after several weeks of purchase and ask your customer to review the product. You can also give them the guarantee to resolve their queries or negative feedback. In a way, you can get valuable reviews for your eCommerce store. </p>\n<h3>13. Focus on Spending</h3>\n<p>You know it very well that any online <strong>paid marketing campaign</strong> can be monitored for spending and RoI. You should keep the focus on ad spending when it comes to promoting your eCommerce store. Though ads are very powerful and are capable of targeting and attracting people, you need to keep a check on spending to avoid your efforts go in vain. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Focus-on-Spending.jpg\" alt=\"Focus on Spending\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1281\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-46089\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Focus-on-Spending.jpg 1920w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Focus-on-Spending-300x200.jpg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Focus-on-Spending-768x512.jpg 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Focus-on-Spending-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Focus-on-Spending-500x334.jpg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Focus-on-Spending-624x416.jpg 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Focus-on-Spending-850x567.jpg 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Focus-on-Spending-366x245.jpg 366w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Focus-on-Spending-450x300.jpg 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" /></p>\n<h3>14. Make Your Store More User-friendly</h3>\n<p>Slow and sluggish website with difficult navigation can keep customers away from your eCommerce shop. In growing competition, if people do not find your website simple, sophisticated, and professional, they will go to other websites quickly. </p>\n<p>You should, therefore, <strong>take care of the following aspects</strong> to make your online shop more customer-friendly:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Give clear and crisp product description along with high-quality, professional photos of products</li>\n<li>Make navigation simple and classify products properly in categories and subcategories</li>\n<li>Include videos and graphics if necessary, but make sure that they do not increase the PLT (Page Load Time)</li>\n<li>Keep checkout and sign-in process simple and straightforward</li>\n</ul>\n<p>These aspects can enable you to attract and engage visitors on your website.</p>\n<h3>15. Emphasize on SEO</h3>\n<p>Last but not least; SEO is still the big factor to <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/seo/10-seo-ranking-factors-boost-google-rankings-2017/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">drive a huge traffic</a> to your eCommerce website. SEO efforts can improve the ranking of your websites on the leading search engines like <b>Google</b> and <b>Bing</b>. However, you need to update the website with relevant and reliable content as well as necessary graphics to meet the latest SEO standards.</p>\n<p>Good user experience and an error-free performance together with SEO campaign can enforce visitors to take a purchasing decision and your store can earn good revenue along with increasing sales figures. </p>\n<h4>Concluding Lines:</h4>\n<p>In a nutshell, eCommerce marketing is a smart and aggressive work. You need to put dedicated efforts and time, but once you apply the right blend of eCommerce marketing ideas, success will not be far away! </p>\n<p>That‚Äôs all for now! Remember, your eCommerce store is an online representative of your business. We do hope that these eCommerce marketing tips will remain handy for you in expanding your business through strengthening online presence. But then, we cannot expect overnight success. Just stick to these strategies, and gradually you will see a visible uptrend in traffic as well as the conversion rate for your eCommerce shop. </p>\n<p>Solwin Infotech has gained fame for offering the best-in-class web design and development services in eCommerce domain. Our expert web developers have served the global clientele with customized and feature-rich eCommerce web solutions.</p>\n<p>Just <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/contact-us/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">drop us a line</a> to build your flawlessly working online shop or learn effective eCommerce marketing strategies to stay ahead of your peers!</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/ecommerce/ecommerce-marketing-strategies/\">15 Actionable Ecommerce Marketing Strategies to Increase Your Online Sales</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/ecommerce/ecommerce-marketing-strategies/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"3\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"20 Best Google Chrome Extensions To Make Your Life 