-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Stay-Focused-500x315.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Stay-Focused-624x394.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Stay-Focused-317x200.png 317w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Stay-Focused-450x284.png 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 634px) 100vw, 634px\" /></p>\n<div style=\"text-align:center\"><a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/stayfocusd/laankejkbhbdhmipfmgcngdelahlfoji\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Install Stay Focused</a></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>20. Tab Wrangler:</h4>\n<p>Tab Wrangler Google chrome extension automatically close idle tabs. It helps your computer from tab overload issue. If you are the kind of person who wants to open lots of tabs while browsing then this extension is useful to you. You can find all the close tabs at Tab Wrangler so, with that, you can quickly open the required tab again. It is a highly configurable extension.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Tab-Wrangler.jpg\" alt=\"Tab Wrangler\" width=\"640\" height=\"400\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-48419\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Tab-Wrangler.jpg 640w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Tab-Wrangler-300x188.jpg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Tab-Wrangler-500x313.jpg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Tab-Wrangler-624x390.jpg 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Tab-Wrangler-320x200.jpg 320w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Tab-Wrangler-450x281.jpg 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /></p>\n<div style=\"text-align:center\"><a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/tab-wrangler/egnjhciaieeiiohknchakcodbpgjnchh\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Install Tab Wrangler</a></div>\n<p>&nbsp;<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/general/best-google-chrome-extensions/\">20 Best Google Chrome Extensions To Make Your Life Easier</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:79:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/general/best-google-chrome-extensions/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:53:\"Top 55+ Magento 2 Extensions For Your Ecommerce Store\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:69:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/magento/top-magento-2-extensions/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:77:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/magento/top-magento-2-extensions/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 25 Oct 2018 14:37:45 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\