og-magento-2-extension-by-solwin-500x1549.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/7-in-1-catalog-magento-2-extension-by-solwin-624x1934.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/7-in-1-catalog-magento-2-extension-by-solwin-850x2634.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/7-in-1-catalog-magento-2-extension-by-solwin-65x200.png 65w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1283px) 100vw, 1283px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/product/magento-2-extensions/7-in-1-catalog-slider-magento-2/\" target=\"_blank\" ><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Details.png\" alt=\"Details\" width=\"165\" height=\"46\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-38513\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>2. Advanced Category Slider</h4>\n<p>Searching the unique way of presenting your product categories. Here is the solution &#8211; <strong>Advanced Category Slider Magento 2 extension</strong>. It will show your product categories with the particular category page with category thumbnail, category name, and description. You can display categories block with an attractive slider on homepage &#038; category pages. It can improve your store performance and usability.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> $49</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/3.-Advanced-Category-Slider-Magento-2-Extension.png\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/3.-Advanced-Category-Slider-Magento-2-Extension.png\" alt=\"3. Advanced Category Slider-Magento 2 Extension\" width=\"1301\" height=\"691\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-47196\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/3.-Advanced-Category-Slider-Magento-2-Extension.png 1301w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/3.-Advanced-Category-Slider-Magento-2-Extension-300x159.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/3.-Advanced-Category-Slider-Magento-2-Extension-768x408.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/3.-Advanced-Category-Slider-Magento-2-Extension-1024x544.png 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/3.-Advanced-Category-Slider-Magento-2-Extension-500x266.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/3.-Advanced-Category-Slider-Magento-2-Extension-624x331.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/3.-Advanced-Category-Slider-Magento-2-Extension-850x451.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/3.-Advanced-Category-Slider-Magento-2-Extension-350x186.png 350w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/3.-Advanced-Category-Slider-Magento-2-Extension-450x239.png 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1301px) 100vw, 1301px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/product/magento-2-extensions/advanced-category-slider-magento-2-extension/\" target=\"_blank\" ><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Details.png\" alt=\"Details\" width=\"165\" height=\"46\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-38513\" /></a></p>\n<h4>3. Advanced Sorting </h4>\n<p>Sorting can help your customers to find their favorite product easily, so ultimately it will increase sales on your website. With the help of <strong>Advanced Sorting &#8211; Magento 2 Extension</strong>, You can add various options like best sellers, most viewed, the biggest saving, rating, etc. Admin can add custom sorting the rule easily from the backend. This extension is easily enabled/disable from the backend. It is the most helpful extension for the store having a large database.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> $79</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Advanced-sorting-by-solwin.jpg\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Advanced-sorting-by-solwin.